pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `formulaire` ( `ID` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `Prenom` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `Nom` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `Profession` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `Email` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `NomEntrepriseDigitale` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `DomaineActivite` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `Url1` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `Url2` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `Url3` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `ChiffreAffaire` int(11) NOT NULL, `ServicesSouhaites` varchar(40) NOT NULL, `BoolNextRdv` tinyint(1) NOT NULL, `NextRdv` date NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`ID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;
